1. Huang Renxun: China is a very important market for NVIDIA, and we hope to continue cooperation in the future;
2. The airdrop of deBridge governance token DBR is now open for collection;
3. Binance liquidity matching project opens the application for certification letter;
4. BTC and ETH options with a nominal value of more than US$2.25 billion will expire and be delivered tomorrow;
5. Binance will launch AERGOUSDT perpetual contract;
6. Bitget Token (BGB) completed its first quarterly destruction, destroying a total of about 30 million BGB;
7. Bhutan plans to develop green mining, and has made "millions of dollars" in profits from investing in cryptocurrencies;
8. Shardeum will conduct TGE on May 5, and details such as airdrops and token distribution will be announced soon;
9. 2 new wallet addresses received 115,000 AAVE and 818,000 UNI from Cumberland;
10. As trading volume declines, Ethereum fees fall to the lowest level in five years;
11. Binance Alpha will launch GOMBLE (GM);
12. Reuters survey: The probability of the United States falling into a recession in the next year is 45%;
13. Binance Alpha launches DARK;
14. Trump: Powell is too slow to act and should have learned from the European Central Bank;
15. Wormhole's first staking reward (SRP1) has been fully distributed and users must claim it before July 15.
